    "description": {
      "zh": ".300win mag（7.62x67B）全金属被甲弹，采用13.9克铅芯、外覆铜被甲和黄铜弹壳。尽管结构简单，该弹种仍能有效击穿中或低防护等级的防弹装甲，并具备可观的停止效应；但这也意味着其在各种表面跳弹概率更高。",
      "en": "A .300 Winchester Magnum (7.62x67B) FMJ cartridge with a 13.9 gram lead core with a copper jacket and brass casing. Despite it's simplicity, this round proves plenty capable of piercing simple to intermediate ballistic armor, as well as having considerable stopping power; however, this also means the round has a high probability of bouncing off various surfaces."
    },
